# Login Page Implementation

## Problem Analysis
- Need a user-friendly login page with visual appeal
- Require support for users with and without passwords
- Need to implement "remember me" functionality
- Require clear error messages for authentication failures
- Need theme support for login page

## Solution Design
- Create user tiles for selection instead of typing usernames
- Implement password field that appears only when needed
- Add animations and transitions for better user experience
- Build "remember me" functionality with secure storage
- Implement error handling with snackbar notifications
- Add theme control from admin panel

